title: Kendra and Tefi are Sliding into Home
description: This week the incredible Tefi Pessoa (@hellotefi) joins Claire (@clairethescare) and Ashley (@ashleyhammm) to talk about the one and only Kendra Wilkinson (@kendrawilkinson) after reading her memoir Sliding into Home. It’s another journey down the Playboy rabbit hole so hold onto your friggin tails.
